%N A393668 Decimal expansion of log(sinh(Pi)/Pi).
%C A393668 Arrives as the k=2 case of the arctanh power sums 2*h(k) = Sum_{n>=2} arctanh(1/n^k).
%H A393668 Ryan Goulden, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.06244">Closed-Form Evaluation of arctanh Power Sums via Infinite Products</a>, arXiv:2602.06244 [math.GM], 2026.
%F A393668 Equals log(sinh(Pi)/Pi) = log(A156648).
%F A393668 Equals 2 * Sum_{n>=2} arctanh(1/n^2).
%F A393668 Equals 2*Sum_{k>=0} (zeta(2*(2*k+1)) - 1) / (2*k+1).
%F A393668 Equals -2*A352527. - _Hugo Pfoertner_, Feb 24 2026
